title: Game Theory and Money: Week 16 Predictions and Playoff Projections
itunes:title: Game Theory and Money: Week 16 Predictions and Playoff Projections
description:
Cynthia Frelund is coming off a week where she correctly picked 10 winners! She ran 10-thousand simulations on every week 16 game, so who does she have coming out on top in Steelers-Saints? Ravens-Chargers? Chiefs-Seahawks? The answers are a click away.


Steelers-Saints (2:40). Buccaneers-Cowboys (8:15). Ravens-Chargers (10:30). Bills-Patriots (14:45). Jaguars-Dolphins (19:40). Bears-49ers (22:00). Broncos-Raiders (24:10). Falcons-Panthers (26:10). FANTASY FUTURES (27:00). THE DOGS (30:30). Chiefs-Seahawks (30:40). Bengals-Browns (36:40). Vikings-Lions (41:00). Giants-Colts (43:20). Rams-Cardinals (46:30). Redskins-Titans (48:35). Texans-Eagles (50:30). CONFIDENCE PICKS (51:50). PLAYOFF PROJECTIONS (55:00).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
